OL,3,CUse of chemotherapy and radiotherapy
OL,4,Cin UK 'lags behind other countries'
OL,6,FTwo new studies show people in the UK
OL,7,Fare treated with chemotherapy and
OL,8,Fradiotherapy less often than in
OL,9,FNorway, Canada and Australia
OL,11,FThe use of in the UK lags behind
OL,12,Fcomparable countries and people wait
OL,13,Ftoo long for treatment, research has
OL,14,Ffound.
OL,16,FTwo new studies part-funded by Cancer
OL,17,FResearch UK and published in the
OL,18,FLancet Oncology show people in the UK
OL,19,Fare treated with chemotherapy and
OL,20,Fradiotherapy less often than in
OL,21,FNorway, Canada and Australia.
