OL,3,CUse of chemotherapy and radiotherapy
OL,4,Cin UK 'lags behind other countries'
OL,6,FThe research was carried out by the
OL,7,FInternational Cancer Benchmarking
OL,8,FPartnership and is the first to
OL,9,Fexamine treatment differences for
OL,10,Feight cancer types across three
OL,11,Fcontinents.
OL,13,FInvestigators looked at more than
OL,14,F780,000 people diagnosed between 2012
OL,15,Fand 2017 with a range of (oesophageal,
OL,16,Fstomach, colon or rectal, which is
OL,17,Fcommonly known as bowel cancer; liver,
OL,18,Fpancreatic, lung and ovarian cancer).
OL,20,FThe studies found:
