OL,6,FIt said countries with more robust
OL,7,Fcancer strategies backed by sufficient
OL,8,Ffunding have seen larger improvements
OL,9,Fin survival than in the UK.
OL,11,FIt also said workforce and capacity
OL,12,Fshortages across the UK health system
OL,13,Fare barriers to delivering
OL,14,Fchemotherapy and radiotherapy.
